<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="light">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About | DinnerHow</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@picocss/pico@2/css/pico.min.css"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        /* Additional Styling */
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #f8f9fa, #e9ecef);
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #555;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        a {
            display: inline-block;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #007bff;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        a:hover {
            color: #0056b3;
        }
        .welcome-container {
            text-align: center; /* Centers the text */
            margin: 20px 0; /* Adds some space above and below */
        }
    
        .welcome-container h1 {
            margin-bottom: 10px; /* Adds spacing between the title and paragraph */
    
        }

        .about-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .about-container img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <main class="container">
        <!-- Navbar -->
        <%- include('../partials/navbar'); %>

        <!-- Welcome Section -->
        <div class="welcome-container">
            <h1>About</h1>
            <p><em>The Cure for "Dinner How?" Syndrome</em></p>
        </div>

        <!-- About Section -->
        <div class="about-container">
            <img src="/images/salami.jpg" alt="Picture of a pizza slice">
            <p>
                Welcome to <strong>DinnerHow.com</strong>, your ultimate escape from the daily "<strong>What should we eat?</strong>" conundrum! Designed for busy Singaporean couples, this playful yet practical website solves the most pressing question of modern life: <strong>“What’s for dinner tonight?”</strong> 
            </p>
            <p>
                We get it. After a long day of meetings, deadlines, and traffic jams, the last thing your brain wants is to debate over <strong>Korean BBQ</strong> or <strong>chicken rice</strong> for the umpteenth time. That's where <strong>DinnerHow.com</strong> swoops in. Think of it as your culinary fairy – effortlessly suggesting dinner ideas tailored to your cravings, diet composition, and location. 
            </p>
            <p>
                Say goodbye to the cognitive overload and hello to delicious, stress-free evenings. Your taste buds (and tired brain) will thank you!
            </p>
            <br>
            <a href="/">Back to Home</a>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
